{"tid":1942882,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日生日 願望係要你嘅一個訂閱 幫我光復香港","createTime":"2020-03-25T10:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T16:33:44.000Z","uid":342854,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3624e72261f4cf4c08722cb147a692f4d6c4ccd1","tid":1942882,"uid":342854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:30:38.000Z","msg":"今日生日嘅我叫<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭仔</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係一位打<span style=\"color: red;\">YouTube</span>戰線嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChannel兩個月都係得3k sub<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChannel主要係放資訊型嘅文宣片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到呢個po嘅你 <br />\n我嘅生日願望係光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以同我一齊打好YouTube戰線<br />\n你嘅一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">訂閱</span></span>好比千句嘅生日快樂<br />\n多謝你地吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJz38RL0J-_cdDuT7XrPj9w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCJz38RL0J-_cdDuT7XrPj9w&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=604c9480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJz38RL0J-_cdDuT7XrPj9w</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9m5dZYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9m5dZYQ.jpg&h=9c2d0356&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e843c3d1ec2d87d957d3851eeedbbf7ed533bba","tid":1942882,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cab93bbd0f486b895f2d80cf18824270696525ad","tid":1942882,"uid":342854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"幫我一齊光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs